data.description: Beautifully unique style and immaculate upkeep.  Kitchen has granite countertops and wood-look porcelain tile flooring which continues to dining area, hallways and bedrooms. Second living has lovely views of the backyard. Large patio area has a pergola for shade. Master bathroom has been updated. Super price for Norris Hills!
